<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id74895050-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s80306"><num value="80306">§ 80306.</num><heading> Restrictions</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="id74895051-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s80306/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">Profit</inline>.—</heading><content>The corporation may not operate for profit.</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="id74895052-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s80306/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">Political Activities</inline>.—</heading><content>The corporation shall be nonpolitical and nonsectarian.</content>
</subsection>
